173
00:10:34.302 --> 00:10:36.602
And these are just examples. There are many others.

174
00:10:38.192 --> 00:10:40.591
In the green box, we have social drivers.

175
00:10:40.632 --> 00:10:44.582
So these are the lived social and economic conditions through

176
00:10:44.612 --> 00:10:48.592
which structural arrangements are experienced by individuals, so

177
00:10:48.632 --> 00:10:51.992
