189
00:11:34.832 --> 00:11:38.692
and places. Social drivers and built environments are among the

190
00:11:38.772 --> 00:11:42.352
mechanisms through which these structures may become

191
00:11:42.392 --> 00:11:46.352
biologically relevant. So even looking at this sort of

192
00:11:46.372 --> 00:11:50.232
in this vertical pathway, you can still see the interconnectedness

193
00:11:50.812 --> 00:11:53.812
and how the structure drives the

194
00:11:54.132 --> 00:11:57.572
social, the built, and further downstream, the cellular

195
00:11:57.592 --> 00:11:58.732
and molecular

196
00:11:58.772 --> 00:12:03.200
mechanisms.So

197
00:12:03.280 --> 00:12:06.640
this slide broadens the framework by emphasizing that

