00:48:51.668 --> 00:48:55.208
SSDOH factors come from? They come from different data sources.

821
00:48:55.268 --> 00:48:59.208
So we have national registry data, state cancer registry data that

822
00:48:59.248 --> 00:49:01.878
can give us information on cancer incidence rates,

823
00:49:03.208 --> 00:49:04.298
mortality rates,

824
00:49:05.228 --> 00:49:07.128
stage of diagnosis, and survival.

