00:49:07.628 --> 00:49:11.608
We also can get our SDOH measures from existing data sources

826
00:49:11.748 --> 00:49:15.288
from the US government. So built environment

827
00:49:15.408 --> 00:49:19.348
from Agency for Toxic Substances and Disease Registry, EPA

828
00:49:19.388 --> 00:49:22.928
data. Most of the social education

829
00:49:23.928 --> 00:49:26.368
and access data come from the US Census, for

