00:54:32.108 --> 00:54:35.688
these SSDOH factors at the macro level, were also

916
00:54:35.698 --> 00:54:38.948
associated with shorter telomere length, suggesting

917
00:54:39.048 --> 00:54:42.628
that this level has its own independent effects

918
00:54:42.748 --> 00:54:45.748
on biology and warrant further investigation.

