00:54:52.788 --> 00:54:56.568
There's been other markers that we've investigated, like allostatic load is a

922
00:54:56.588 --> 00:54:59.188
project that Adina and Jesse are involved in.

923
00:54:59.568 --> 00:55:03.247
So these are just some examples of how you can integrate this data for biologic

924
00:55:03.368 --> 00:55:03.868
studies.

925
00:55:05.628 --> 00:55:05.948
So

926
00:55:06.928 --> 00:55:07.968
one of the differences

927
00:55:08.888 --> 00:55:12.648
between studies when is the selection of which

