00:55:21.008 --> 00:55:24.968
SSDOH variables. So if you want help narrowing down

931
00:55:25.028 --> 00:55:28.828
which variables might be most relevant for your analysis,

932
00:55:29.008 --> 00:55:32.478
one way you can do that is through the application of these

933
00:55:32.508 --> 00:55:36.188
empiric methodologies, like a neighborhood-wide association

