00:55:41.528 --> 00:55:43.888
And I have one example of that here that we worked

937
00:55:43.968 --> 00:55:47.654
on.So our particular research question was:

938
00:55:47.844 --> 00:55:51.744
what neighborhood SSDOH factors are related to aggressive

