00:56:45.884 --> 00:56:49.044
SSDOH factors came up within each race ethnic group.

954
00:56:49.744 --> 00:56:52.604
So in this particular data set, there were

955
00:56:52.964 --> 00:56:56.824
900 cases of Black men with aggressive disease versus not,

956
00:56:57.264 --> 00:56:58.084
and in White men,

957
00:56:59.004 --> 00:57:02.704
close to 6,500 cases with aggressive disease versus not.

958
00:57:03.344 --> 00:57:06.644
We applied an NWAS approach, which is similar to genome-wide

959
00:57:06.684 --> 00:57:10.164
association study approach, where you apply

960
00:57:10.804 --> 00:57:14.384
