00:58:20.984 --> 00:58:24.664
if these variables had any clinical utility in

981
00:58:24.684 --> 00:58:25.704
prostate cancer,

982
00:58:26.684 --> 00:58:30.444
particularly in the context of biomarkers that we know are associated with

