00:59:07.764 --> 00:59:11.704
biomarker, together with some of these SSDOH

994
00:59:11.724 --> 00:59:15.024
variables, could improve the predictive probability of prostate

995
00:59:15.084 --> 00:59:17.284
cancer in this particular sample.

996
00:59:18.544 --> 00:59:20.204
And for this study,

997
00:59:21.164 --> 00:59:24.304
we applied lasso machine learning approaches,

998
00:59:24.904 --> 00:59:28.824
and we looked at each of the SSDOH variables from the NWAS

